| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2342 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6746f795-2c53-5e5f-9fc1-8aafa17b5c4a"
